description	"Mitth'raw'nuruodo

Class: Hero
Brief Overview: 
An agile, pistol-wielding commander/medic hybrid with force power resistance.

^2Weaponry:
- Pistol (3)
- Frag Grenades (2)
- Sonic Detonators (2)
- Fire Grenade (1)

^8Attributes:
- Rally
- Tactical Acumen (Can view ally stats)
- Energized Jump (Force Jump 1)
- Ysalimari (Force Block 2)

^6Inventory:
- Binoculars
- Bacta (+25 HP to self)
- Big Bacta (+50 HP to self)
- Seeker Drone

^3Abilities:
- First Aid [While in Melee, press 'Use' on allies to recover their health and armor]
- Dodge (2) [Class Special 1]
- Flipkick (2) [Double-jump off players and surfaces]
- Advanced Deductive ^3Abilities (Force Sense 3)

Mitth'raw'nuruodo, better known as 'Thrawn', was recognized across the galaxy as a brilliant and ruthless military strategist. He believed that in order to achieve victory in war, one must know their enemy. As such, he dedicated himself to understanding the philosophy, art, and culture of his opponents."